WEBVTT

00:08.080 --> 00:09.713
If you became a superhero,

00:09.748 --> 00:11.248
you had to design your own costume,

00:11.300 --> 00:12.499
would you go full mask,

00:12.551 --> 00:13.500
or would you just wear the thing

00:13.552 --> 00:15.052
that just covers your eyes?

00:15.087 --> 00:16.386
Oof.

00:16.422 --> 00:17.838
I mean, I feel like in real life,

00:17.890 --> 00:19.473
I'd want to go full mask most of the time.

00:19.508 --> 00:21.391
[Laughter]

00:21.427 --> 00:22.593
What about you?

00:22.645 --> 00:23.644
For cool factor,

00:23.679 --> 00:25.095
I would want to go full mask.

00:25.147 --> 00:27.014
See, I don't buy it out of you.

00:27.066 --> 00:28.982
You're such a fame whore.

00:29.018 --> 00:31.068
He'd wear no mask at all. Yeah.

00:31.103 --> 00:32.686
[Laughing] Yeah, right?

00:32.738 --> 00:34.488
There's no way you'd wear any sort of mask.

00:34.523 --> 00:37.441
You'd want the grandeur and the applause

00:37.493 --> 00:38.909
and everything that goes with it.

00:38.944 --> 00:40.494
On my costume, like, my full name

00:40.529 --> 00:41.745
would be emblazoned on there,

00:41.780 --> 00:43.413
yeah, so everybody knew that it was me.

00:43.449 --> 00:45.833
My archenemy will
never find my loved ones.

00:45.868 --> 00:47.668
Kids, daddy wants a modicum of fame.

00:47.703 --> 00:50.254
Don't you understand that
your lives are worth that?

00:50.289 --> 00:51.588
They just got to be a little more careful.

00:51.624 --> 00:52.623
Yeah.

00:52.675 --> 00:53.624
Yeah?

00:53.676 --> 00:54.842
[Laughter]

00:54.877 --> 00:55.843
[Heroic music]

