Could y'all tell me what this is from?

10:08.429 --> 10:10.512
Oh, I recognize that.
You recognize that, Mike?

10:10.564 --> 10:12.731
- Iron Man.
- Exactly, so hold on.

10:12.766 --> 10:15.067
I'm gonna put you on
the spot and go deeper.

10:15.102 --> 10:17.235
Let me see

10:17.271 --> 10:18.904
if this is the real mecca.

10:18.939 --> 10:20.355
Check this out.

10:20.407 --> 10:22.274
Akira.

10:22.326 --> 10:25.110
Oh, that's good. Oh, wow.

10:25.162 --> 10:27.529
- Incredible Hulk.
- Web of Spider-Man.

10:27.581 --> 10:29.081
Oh, wow... okay, okay.

10:29.116 --> 10:31.667
How about this one?

10:31.702 --> 10:33.535
<i>Black Panther, Jungle Tales.</i>

10:33.587 --> 10:34.786
<i>Dark Knight Returns.</i>

10:34.838 --> 10:36.171
Okay, okay, okay.

10:36.206 --> 10:37.422
[Chuckles]

10:37.458 --> 10:39.124
All right, here we go.

10:39.176 --> 10:41.793
<i>Wolverine, X-Men 211, I believe.</i>

10:41.845 --> 10:44.129
- John Romita, Jr.
- Yeah, I'm pretty sure.

10:44.181 --> 10:46.465
And this one is Daredevil, isn't it?

10:46.517 --> 10:48.350
Oh, man, I ain't getting over on you.

10:48.385 --> 10:49.601
[Laughter]

10:49.637 --> 10:51.186
So y'all official.

10:51.221 --> 10:52.971
You know, I come in here
like I'm all official,

10:53.023 --> 10:55.891
trying to test your...
but that's great, man.

